definitions.definition: The sound of a quiet cough or of clearing one's throat .
An exclamation or cough to get attention .
examples: Ahem ! Could we please get started?

definitions.definition: An exclamation of disapproval or annoyance .
examples: Ahem ! In case you didn't notice, I did my share of the work, too.
I really ( ahem !) liked the chocolate broccoli surprise.
